comments: Williams (CHI) makes marginal contact to Embiid's (PHI) body after the release of his jump shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, it was determined the on-court ruling was overturned to PHI ball.

Thybulle (PHI) does not make contact to LaVine's (CHI) arm on his driving shot attempt.
Young (CHI) makes contact to Embiid's (PHI) arm and contact affects his SQBR.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact to LaVine's (CHI) body after the release of his jump shot attempt.
